      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/elijah-crane",
      "text": "Grateful to my colleagues for unanimously adopting my amendment to the State Department appropriations bill today.\n\nAmerican taxpayers should not be paying for foreign military training unless we are fully reimbursed.\n\nProud to fight for #AZ02. https://t.co/XWus5vDO6n",
