      "ownerName": "Elijah Crane",
      "ownerType": "Congress",
      "countryId": "usa",
      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/elijah-crane",
      "text": "Today, I spoke on the floor in support of my amendment to the State Department appropriations bill.\n\nMy provision prohibits funds in the Act from subsidizing military training that foreign nations should be paying for themselves.\n\nPleased to report it was adopted unanimously. https://t.co/SG1snn3cCq",
