      "ownerType": "Congress",
      "countryId": "usa",
      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/elijah-crane",
      "text": "This evening, I joined @jsolomonReports and @AmandaHead to review several major national concerns.\n\nWe covered the alarming developments involving Jack Smith, the ongoing fight to protect the Fourth Amendment, and updates on the SAVE America Act. https://t.co/A3KHc2eKKd",
